query:
SELECT 
  r.id, 
  r.name, 
  r.date,
  FROM_UNIXTIME(r.date/1000) as readable_date
FROM trip_routes r 
JOIN trips t ON r.tripId = t.id 
WHERE (t.name LIKE '%Slovakia%' OR t.destination LIKE '%Slovakia%')
ORDER BY r.id;
